    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A semivernacular medieval Chinese literary genre often featuring Buddhist content; the term means "transformation text." The genre developed as a popularization of Buddhist doctrine through storytelling, pictorial representation, and performance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
